# BarberPro Project Context

BarberPro is a **Malaysia-first, multi-tenant barber shop management SaaS** built as a pnpm monorepo.

## Monorepo Apps

| App | Package | Domain | Status |
|---|---|---|---|
| `apps/web-shop` | `@barberpro/web-shop` | `shop.barberpro.my` | Active ‚Äî barber shop owners & staff |
| `apps/web-admin` | `@barberpro/web-admin` | `admin-pro.barberpro.my` | Active ‚Äî BarberPro super admin |
| `apps/web-customer` | `@barberpro/web-customer` | `barberpro.my` | Active ‚Äî end customers |
| `apps/mobile-customer` | `@barberpro/mobile-customer` | App Store / Play Store | Planned Phase 4 |
| `apps/mobile-staff` | `@barberpro/mobile-staff` | App Store / Play Store | Planned Phase 5 |

## Shared Packages

| Package | Purpose | Status |
|---|---|---|
| `packages/db` | Supabase clients + shared queries | Exists |
| `packages/auth` | Auth helpers, getAuthContext | Exists |
| `packages/ui` | shadcn/ui design tokens + shared web components | Exists |
| `packages/ui-native` | NativeWind React Native components | Planned |
| `packages/types` | Shared TypeScript types | Exists (placeholder) |
| `packages/config` | Shared tsconfig base | Exists |
| `packages/env` | Typed env helpers | Exists |
| `packages/notifications` | Expo push notification helpers | Planned |

## Backend

- **Supabase** ‚Äî single project, PostgreSQL, RLS for tenant isolation
- **Stripe** ‚Äî subscription billing for barber shop operators
- **Vercel** ‚Äî deployment platform, separate project per web app
- **Expo EAS** ‚Äî mobile app builds and OTA updates

## Current Status
All phases (0‚Äì6) have been implemented. Production hardening, shared packages, all web apps, mobile app scaffolds, and enterprise features are in place.

